OL,6,FLabour deputy leader Angela Rayner has
OL,7,Fpledged 140,000 low-paid women workers
OL,8,Fin Scotland will be better off thanks
OL,9,Fto the party's plans to tackle the
OL,10,F"scourge" of insecure work.
OL,12,FWith Labour promising improved
OL,13,Femployment rights for workers if it
OL,14,Fwins next week's General Election, Ms
OL,15,FRayner is to campaign in Scotland on
OL,16,FFriday, higlighting how the plans
OL,17,Fwould help female workers.
